<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="B" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Bolingbroke" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Bolingbroke</orth> (O. Edd. mostly <emph>Bullingbroke</emph>). 1) <emph>Henry B.,</emph> afterwards King Henry IV: <bibl n="shak. r2 1.1.124" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 I, 1, 124</bibl> etc. etc. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 1.3.137" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A I, 3, 137</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.1.64" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 64</bibl> etc. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 2.5.83" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A II, 5, 83</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 2.2.21" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B II, 2, 21</bibl>. -- 2) <emph>Roger B.,</emph> the conjurer: <bibl n="shak. 2h6 1.2.76" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B I, 2, 76</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>